title: VRExpress
author: VRExpress
content: Do you think that NFT projects will still be able to catch up in the future? I am presently looking into an NFT project that almost all new and old projects are in partnership with, the name of this project is called XP Network. https://xp.network/No single blockchain have been left out of XP Network, this project can do pretty well in the next bull market.
